{
  "stem": "4361.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the SS told me, Fraulein, in a very polite tone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so, I thought I'll see my mother the next day or the day after.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Thank god, she wouldn't have to walk as we eventually had to walk for about another three or four miles.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because, as I know now, this was all in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they were taking us to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "By the time we arrived to Birkenau, to this other camp-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, I am going to backtrack now because I suddenly remembered the 'Arbeit macht frei' sign.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Yeah, the 'Arbeit macht frei' sign-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] anyway, there was that sign, as you know, the motto of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The sign-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when they took us from the train to-- well, it was beginning to dawn, no, no, not quite dawn.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's very strange.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, they were the [GERMAN], the night workers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were-- From the train, they took us through a gate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I told you that the flames were shooting and really, illuminating much of the place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I looked up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a big, wrought-iron-- a big sign which said, 'Arbeit macht frei,' 'work gives you freedom.' Well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The mockery of it, it didn't hit me then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, that was our reception into Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't know what it meant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Arbeit macht frei?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What-- well, we are supposed to work, but-- but this couldn't be Kenyermezo because the sign is in German.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you know, people do nothing rationally when the panic, the fear, when the heartbeat is, is, is, is mad, when, when, when blood runs cold, you don't know what it is.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's another planet, another world.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
